Flurry - blade technique
------------------------------------------------------------
Speed is the swashbucklers' greatest advantage in combat,
and nowhere is that more obvious than the flurry skill. By
concentrating on the offensive, a swashbuckler can take
advantage of the slightest openings and strike at his enemy
more often.

Every successful Flurry proc grants one extra swing. Hero-level
Swashbucklers can gain a second extra swing, and Legend-level
Swashbucklers can gain a third. Rank provides most of each chance;
character level adds a smaller bonus.

GL: 12
SP: 8 / proc, reduced by Flow
command: starttech flurry
duration: technique mode
